               stealing, on the <rs id="t18260406-64-cd341" type="crimeDate">29th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260406-64-off340 t18260406-64-cd341"></join>, 3 wooden boxes, value 2s., and 4lbs. of segars, value 6s. 5s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18260406-64-victim428" type="victimName">
                  William Ferdinand 
                  Sintenis
               <interp inst="t18260406-64-victim428" type="surname" value="Sintenis"></interp>
